t-range forces also\naffect orbital flips, progressively reducing the range of Itot within which\nflips are possible as the intensity of these forces increases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Sep 2014 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Jan 2015 22:46:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
