ories. This individual particle motion correction,\nin combination with weighting of Fourier components to account for increasing\nradiation damage in later frames, can be used to improve 3-D maps from single\nparticle cryo-EM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Sep 2014 01:24:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Feb 2015 19:25:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Oct 2015 02:24:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-23"}
